5A327CBE.Line1.7F064: Primus, the communing pillar is quiet. I don’t know what has happened. We slaughtered the slaves like you said, but still the Three are silent. What have the faithful done to displease them?

63305C6D.VoiceDir3.7F064: Alarm. Shouts out to someone in the distance, then is cut off and attacked.

C93BE2EB.VoiceDir1.7F064: Concerned. Speaking to someone in authority

F426F640.Line3.7F064: No! Don’t go near it! We can no longer control – (pained screams)
